## Best Pracices
Here are s


use only tools and libraries that are essential.
dding more tools and libraries that might be useful in the future just adds up complexity and slows down your development.


```
project/
  controllers/
    users.js
  util/
    plugin.js
  middlewares/
    auth.js
  models/
    user.js
  routes/
    user.js
    router.js
  public/
    js/
    css/
    img/
  views/
    users/
      index.jade
  tests/
    users/
      create-user-test.js
      update-user-test.js
      get-user-test.js
  .gitignore
  app.js
  package.json
  ```


